column5: I was interested in going to Kapikik this summer and I understand that there are some other cabins on Kapikik Lake outside of Clark's that are owned by the residents of the Cat Lake Native Reservation. Does anyone know a site, email, or contact for them? Nothing against Clark's, they just did not have the slots available for me this year.
They have 29 outposts pick another one.All of them hold amazing fishing
The native cabins are not for rent.They are for personal use only
